      <title>尽管移民激增，新西兰的信用卡消费却下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/new-zealand-s-card-spending-drops-even-as-immigration-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰的消费支出在 2023 年最后三个月放缓，尽管移民人数创纪录，但借记卡和信用卡支出仍较上年同期下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/new-zealand-s-card-spending-drops-even-as-immigration-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:52:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元复苏抵消中东危机影响油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强和更广泛的避险基调抵消了对中东紧张局势升级的担忧，包括伊朗支持的胡塞叛乱分子在红海持续袭击船只，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:51:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称中国将考虑发行 1,390 亿美元特别债券以实施更多刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-16/china-weighs-more-stimulus-with-139b-of-special-bonds-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，中国正在考虑根据所谓的特别主权债券计划发行 1 万亿元人民币（合 1,390 亿美元）的新债券，因为政府寻求更多资金来资助其提振经济的努力。吉尔·迪西斯在彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-16/china-weighs-more-stimulus-with-139b-of-special-bonds-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
